694
00:42:10,950 --> 00:42:12,280
Takže,

695
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:13,470
Ya Yin.

696
00:42:13,990 --> 00:42:17,270
Chcem, aby si zajtra šla
na prax do spoločnosti.

697
00:42:17,750 --> 00:42:18,800
Čože?

